summary: Developed Neeva’s first-time user experience, including its homepage, account creation, and premium subscription flows
Revamped Neeva’s homepage to fully support multiple languages, helping drive expansion into Europe and Asia
Constructed an end-to-end pipeline using DALL-E and Stable Diffusion to serve generated thumbnails for search results
Led A/B tests which involved coordinating with design, building UIs, and driving launch discussions, contributing to a 10x increase in users in 2022
